name: The First Of These | P0034 #pennydrops
description:
A Dada/Burroughs-inspired cut-up poem, created from an 1873 copy of The Times newspaper, on the reverse of an 1873 penny. This 1/1 comes with its physical penny equivalent for the first buyer. Please contact us via Twitter @quietbritacc to arrange free shipping.
